{"tid":84514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家搭地鐵坐低係咪要問坐係旁邊既人比唔比坐先？","createTime":"2017-01-17T15:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T15:58:47.000Z","uid":13282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3753936fb1e4b782b00e3744c5fbbf0bf9a150b7","tid":84514,"uid":13282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"痴線，4人位，坐左2個，<br />\n我同朋友2個人見中間有位咪坐落去<br />\n一坐低左邊條友(1X-2X歲)就發出好不肖既聲，<br />\n跟住我望一望佢，見又唔係迫住佢，<br />\n佢又望住部電話，咪以為佢係不肖佢手機入面既野，<br />\n過左2個站我朋友見到條友唔知做咩，<br />\n問我係咪迫住佢，一係坐開d(睇落我無坐過界，同埋我同佢之間重有空位)，<br />\n咁我照坐開d同縮埋咁坐，<br />\n到佢起身落車，我咪坐佢個位，<br />\n因為之前我朋友比位我坐開d，搞到好似壓住佢旁邊果個，<br />\n咪諗住坐開少少<br />\n跟住條友回頭望我，用d好似話你on9既笑容對住我，<br />\n再對我搖頭，跟住落左車，<br />\n下？個位你既？你落左車唔可以坐？<br />\n中間唔可以坐人？4人位唔可以坐4個人？<br />\n我迫到你咪同我講囉，我撞到你咪同我講囉，<br />\n我坐過界咪出聲囉，有必要咁？<br />\n事後有個比你大成倍既人坐埋黎都唔覺得迫<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講既係，對後來坐埋黎果位人兄講聲對唔住，<br />\n因為我果刻堅嬲，但唔係話緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e3ca67f211d86f3d9bd9b905623a0555e8d0c8","tid":84514,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T15:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset